entries.femaleVariant: Great! You checkin' out again?!
Wanna be in the driver's seat.
I do, and I don't like it.
'Course I can see. Want me to hand over the keys.
I wanna save your life.
Won't take a risk this big with someone she still sees in merc diapers.
Yeah, I get it. And don't like it one bit. I'm still goin' strong.
C'mon, face the facts.
Right about that, but that's why I'll bring Rogue. She's not rusted through just yet. Plus, she owes me.
I warned you.
And you can't stand on your own two feet.
While I'm good to go, body listens to me.
See what I'm gettin' at?
Hanako's offer's on the table.
I'm sorry, whose?
Oh, cut the crap! She actually has power, could be our ticket.
What about Panam? She offered help.
Rogue? I dunno... You honestly think it could work?
Our ticket, huh? OK, I see your angle.
You think workin' with the corpocunt is gonna sweeten the deal.
Well, let me tell ya somethin' – the corpo kleptocracy is not an option!
Yeah, one-way ticket to the city morgue.
That 'Saka cunt's scrambled your circuits.
Listen up, V. Those guys are trailer tuggers.
An assault on Arasaka's just not another convoy to 'jack.
You already tried this with amateurs... Both know how that ended.
And you... tried it with pros. Didn't end any fucking better.
entries.maleVariant: And you tried it with pros. Didn't end any fucking better.

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, I know you and Panam got a thing going. I get it, I do.
But that's what makes it such a shitty idea. You don't wanna rope her into this.
Made the same mistake myself, once.
With her experience? Her resources? Her connections?
Won't find anyone better in NC.
Johnny...
It's gotta work! We breach the tower, Alt cracks open Mikoshi, then I fuck up that--
Ughhh...
Gotta stop you, dickhead. What's your scheme? This is my body, I make the calls.
Not this time.
Agh, Johnny...
Jesus, look at you. Can't even--
Need more time, need to--
Don't you get it?! Time is something we are fresh out of!
You even believe this could work?
My call, not yours.
Still got Hanako's offer to consider.
I dunno... Need time to think it over.
You really think Rogue gives you a shot?
What about Panam? She wanted to help.
This is my call, not yours!
I dunno... Gotta think it through.
Our one hope is sittin' at the Afterlife right now and her name is Rogue.
Rogue and I will handle this. Just like we used to.
Think that could work?
What about Panam? She wanted to help too.
Hanako's offer is still on the table.
I'll convince her. After all, we know a thing or two about ops like this.
Pop some pseudoendotrizine, scooch and lemme get behind the wheel.
It's our only chance.
I can ask Rogue myself.
W-what're you doing?
I'll get us to fuckin' Mikoshi.
Do I even need you? Could ask Rogue myself.
entries.maleVariant: Do I even need you? I could ask Rogue myself.

entries.femaleVariant: Shit, we could be hours from it, now, V.
Uh-huh. How, exactly?
Without that porcelain cunt's help, that's for damn sure.
Don't stand a chance without help.
With me, it'd be just like old times.
You don't want those people involved, their lives on the line, possibly on your conscience.
We'll blast our way into 'Saka Tower just like we did back in the day. Then find the way inside Mikoshi.
What am I doing?
I'm showin' you what it's like to feel fuckin' trapped.
Asked you. Warned you. But you've insisted on not giving a shit.
Now this porcelain cunt's gonna use you in her fancy scheme.
Haven't agreed to anything yet.
What's the problem? We know where Mikoshi is.
Got a problem with that?
And what's that give us?
Fuck off. Haven't agreed to anything yet.
'Cause that's what we wanted. We know where to find...
The gates to Mikoshi? Yeah, beneath 'Saka Tower.
But I know you still don't understand how these leeches operate.
She met you face to face. She revealed her plan.
She's sunk her teeth deep into you. Not gonna be able to pry yourself out.
Wha... Huh?
We got no other choice.
Know exactly how corporats operate. Don't play games.
I know perfectly well how they operate. You don't play ball willingly, they force you.
Got any other ideas? I'd love to hear 'em!
What's that fuckin' give us?!
Dunno yet.
We can storm Arasaka Tower.
Could ask the nomads for help.
Could ask the nomads for help.
Well, could ask the Aldecaldos to lend a hand.
Johnny...
I don't know yet! Haven't decided anything!
Don't wanna team up with Hanako? Can't blame you. Neither do I.
We make some calls, load up on iron, then we kick down the door to Arasaka Tower.
You wanna lead an all-out assault on 'Saka Tower...?
Jesus Christ. You can barely stand on your own two feet!
But... Johnny...
Whaddaya say to doin' things the old-fashioned way?
They don't play these kinda games! Don't invite you for a meal at a restaurant with a fucking grand piano!
entries.maleVariant: They don't play these kinda games! Don't invite you for a meal at a restaurant with a fuckin' grand piano!

entries.femaleVariant: Hey, you relax…
If we stand to gain anything from anyone inside Arasaka, it's her! So maybe…
V?
No?! Then shut up and back off!
Hey, you'd better relax.
Then we got a real fuckin' problem, don't we?!
I… am… fine…
Maybe she'd have stuck her neck out for you a half century ago. But now? I don't see it.
